{"tid":809542,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"莫迪歷︰C朗話我值得贏歐聯最佳球員","createTime":"2018-09-07T09:18:35.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-07T10:19:01.000Z","uid":20634,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"28c5b27c81d1b3b82a7540f741ea835fccb4e0b3","tid":809542,"uid":20634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-07T09:18:35.000Z","msg":"克羅地亞與葡萄牙在周四晚上演友賽，最終兩隊打成1︰1，賽後「格仔兵」中場莫迪歷表示，C朗已恭喜他贏得上屆歐聯最佳球員，並讚他值得獲獎。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n在早前舉行的歐聯頒獎禮，莫迪歷擊敗C朗及沙拿當選最佳球員，<span style=\"color: red;\">有指C朗當晚未有現身是因對此結果感到不滿</span>，而其經理人文迪斯亦批評結果是「荒謬」。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n不過莫迪歷透露，雖然C朗在周四友賽休息缺陣，但已私下傳短訊恭喜他獲獎，並讚他實至名歸︰「他恭喜我，並表示很想與我快些見面。」<br />\n<br />\n二人同樣入選國際足協的世界足球先生最後3強，將再爭逐大獎︰「很高興可進身另一大獎的最後階段，我與C朗關係很好，將來亦一樣，<span style=\"color: red;\">個人獎項很重要但我不會迷戀它</span>。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 」(<a href=\"http://Goal.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FGoal.com&d=y3Nr2Xfmn7RCtyCHc53wQY9%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=3c612834\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">Goal.com</a>)"},{"pid":"ddf773992190bb35803a40acd283407c57bc78a6","tid":809542,"uid":163937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-07T10:14:49.000Z","msg":"風度翩翩牙朗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b51a274d602c99df5976385db9a046e719cbba75","tid":809542,"uid":47268,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-07T10:16:10.000Z","msg":"怨婦朗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f994ae4be135aa1ea65e45496a799ccd0c1cc19f","tid":809542,"uid":34571,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-07T10:19:01.000Z","msg":"見面果陣叫莫迪拎埋個獎出黎"}]}